      "citation_id": "[CITATION_1]",
      "span_text": "Even after 6 years, the investigation of [CITATION_1] remains one of the rare examples where with the help of proteomics one protein (ESAT-6) was separated into eight protein species and four of them were analysed with 100% sequence coverage, allowing a real protein species differentiation and a correlation to different functions."
    }
